{"tid":1497121,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚嬲 講咗幾多次太空卡","createTime":"2019-08-22T23:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T06:35:06.000Z","uid":28759,"like":62,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1444c4a120d128f2e8e9e54c5baf8b42812dad14","tid":1497121,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:15:05.000Z","msg":"文宣組俾人起底啦<br />\n開心未<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捨得買太空卡未啊</span></span></strong><br />\n四十蚊保平安<br />\n<br />\n問題從來都唔係俾人拉<br />\n係啲狗知道你喺個 grp 到<br />\n就會用各種程序滋擾你<br />\n<br />\n告唔入？<br />\n拉你返去玩返 48 個鐘先<br />\n<br />\n冇犯法？<br />\n起你底幫你訂 pizza 恐嚇你<br />\n<br />\n記唔記有個女仔<br />\n喺 ig 鬧狗都俾人跟蹤<br />\n記唔記得學生會成員<br />\n收恐嚇信話要斬佢全家？<br />\n<br />\n唔好以為唔上前綫就冇事<br />\n俾人斬得最甘嗰啲<br />\n一個痴連儂牆<br />\n一個路過<br />\n幾個居民嚟<br />\n<br />\n依家啲狗係乜人都搞<br />\n男女老幼永不落空<br />\n仲抱住僥倖心態<br />\n覺得啲狗唔會搞你嘅<br />\n會唔會太天真？<br />\n<br />\n冇太空卡嘅<br />\n同我退出所有反送中群組<br />\n最好就 delete 埋 ac<br />\n開咗太空卡先好入返<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇太空卡 = 送頭</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n快啲 google / 叫朋友幫你整<br />\n兩個幾月都買唔到電話卡<br />\n你話你地抵唔抵屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲買"},{"pid":"f539c5160ca9c193a34c3d5bfda10e6270d8182c","tid":1497121,"uid":69334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:22:32.000Z","msg":"3 既trihalo好似25蚊攪得掂，年卡可以用1年"},{"pid":"bf3bba6b90dc943aa7a60049183b4c991b3987b6","tid":1497121,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:23:17.000Z","msg":"ching 講緊tg?"},{"pid":"756127396cb13c4beb98d3507086e8dbf5f4510c","tid":1497121,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf3bba6b90dc943aa7a60049183b4c991b3987b6","tid":1497121,"uid":33618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:23:17.000Z","msg":"ching 講緊tg?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T23:36:07.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"86b00ec